item.title: Delete please
item.dc:creator: @paymon paymon
item.description:
@paymon wrote:

[quote=“EmulousGuru, post:65, topic:367169”]Coders should get more donations that hoster, and you, Paymon, shouldn’t get any, unless you are participating in the evolution of the server.

It sounds like you are making a team, to where you make money, and you don’t do anything except have powers on the server.

Also, you said you have multiple features, which you haven’t proved:

would u like the chance of coding and hosting for elusionx our vps is crashing so we need a dedicated hoster and these our the things i would like to add we already have a pro coder called nick but we need more to make this work:

Yeah that is what i hate about most server, they are all the same, i am going for something different. What you ask?
Well let me show you…
Summoning
Hunter
Construction
Full screen mode
Many real quests from runescape
Custom quests
All minigames from runescape
Some custom Minigames
Full 62 wave jad thing (forgot name sorry)
full working godwars

As you can see my friends i am making this server as original and different ad possible. But we can not do this all alone, we need more coders. Yes, it is true that Nick our proud coder is coding for us, but we need a more professional and original coder group. You will all get a custom yell tag and maybe even some sort of crown. Also i will see about donations and you will get credits each and every one of you.

To look at my dev team plz look at this:
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,463354.0.html

Prove some of that, fix the donation amount, and show some progress of what you have/actually can do, and I may join the team.[/quote]

Hi, i am sorry if you miss read, i did not mention (dev team or message) about me getting any of the donations, though i did mention that the hoster will get 30% Proof:

we need hoster ~(will get 30% of all donations + head admin or co-owner spot)~

Also yes it is correct that the other 70% will be going to the coders,website and advertisement.
Secondly i would only like experienced coders on the team this is the reason why i messaged you my freind.
